  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SourceBeginExportNodeEventListener
    Define a listener that responds to the Source's "disconnected" event.
    SourceConnectedEventListener
    Define a listener that responds to the Source's "connected" event.
    SourceDisconnectedEventListener
    Define a listener that responds to the Source's "disconnected" event.
    SourceEndExportFinalNodeEventListener
    Listener that responds to the Sources's "end export final node" event.
    SourceEndExportNodeEventListener
    Define a listener that responds to the Source's "end export node" event.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PdfParserAttributeSetterListener
    This listener reads the content from a PDF (your file must be a PDF) and sets properties based on regex information.
    QueueItemEventSourceListener
    Will take a queueItem and check to see if it has any associations that are versions.
    SplitPDFListener
    Based on the configured attributes, take in a start page and an end page to split a particular node on.
